Author: Mathias Fussenegger <f.mathias@zignar.net>
Date:   Tue Feb 27 10:14:01 2024 +0100

    Load functions without guice
    
    This will make it possible to use Functions within guice modules like
    the `MetadataModule`, to use them in `fromXContent` implementations like
    `ForeignTable.fromXContent` - to parse expressions into symbols.
    
    The registration mechanism is quite similar to from before, except that
    the guice modules are replaced with components implementing a
    `FunctionsProvider`. These `FunctionsProvider` are loaded via a service
    loader to trigger the registration of the functions.

